%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">小人物的生活</a>和感情为主题，充满浓浓的“台味”。为了更加贴合该剧的“市井”气息，海报中漫画的部分高度还原拍摄地台北一条普通的街道，甚至连悬挂的招牌和路边停放的机车都“神还原”出来。如此细致的海报，甚至引发网友纷纷猜测这是台北的哪条路，并相约去该地点“朝圣”。</p><p><img src="http://p33.qhimg.com/t01d020475b196fb047.jpg?size=550x372"></p><p>剧照</p></div>  <footer>  <p class=tip_quick>文章内容由搜索引擎自动发现并显示为快照，不代表360新闻的立场和观点，<a target=_blank class=viewsource href="http://comic.people.com.cn/n/2015/0416/c122366-26855608.html">查看原文</a></p>      </footer> </article> <section class=sohu_cy> <div id=SOHUCS sid='63ef9d0f804958dc81034d3a076b487f'></div><script id=changyan_mobile_js charset="utf-8" src="http://changyan.sohu.com/upload/mobile/wap-js/changyan_mobile.js?client_id=cyrTywwWs&conf=prod_c56aa5a54e89138d855c5ca9b31470a0" ></script> </section>  <aside id="next-news"> <h3><em>吃货都是孤独的</em>的其它新闻:</h3> <ul>    <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E5%90%83%E8%B4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E7%9A%84&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=5&amp;m=4c1c419411338dce7d3a17a58e37969a8ebcecd3&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.163.com%2F14%2F0819%2F15%2FA418OB5100063KE8.html" data-pos="1"> <b>孤独</b>美食家 <b>吃货</b>玩转日本十座城市 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E5%90%83%E8%B4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E7%9A%84&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=6&amp;m=7828b9eacad852b780d6359519cc4fba36c7f52e&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Facg.178.com%2F201405%2F194569708010_s.html" data-pos="2"> 舌尖上的<b>吃货</b>大叔,《<b>孤独</b>的美食家》第4季7月9日播出 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E5%90%83%E8%B4%A7%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%A4%E7%8B%AC%E7%9A%84&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=7&amp;m=00407e99b3f1df8c40aedda4bb843e22ee98619c&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ce.cn%2Fnews%2F201412%2F04%2Ft20141204_4048991.shtml" data-pos="3"> "<b>吃货</b>"赵文瑄出演土豆版《<b>孤独</b>的美食家》男一号 </a>  </ul> </aside>  <div class=mask style="display:none"></div> <div class="open-in-browser-tip" style="display:none"> <p>好无奈，微信君不让直接下载，别担心，点击<b>右上角</b>，选择“<b>在浏览器中打开</b>”就能下载啦~</p> <a class=close href="javascript:;"><img src="http://p3.qhimg.com/d/inn/a8960a66/close.png"></a> </